&lt;h2&gt;System Requirements&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="system-requirements"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#system-requirements" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Node.js 16+ or Python 3.8+&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4GB RAM minimum&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10GB free disk space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
