&lt;h2&gt;Troubleshooting&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="troubleshooting"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a href="#troubleshooting" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Common issues and solutions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Connection errors&lt;/strong&gt;: Check your API key and network settings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Version conflicts&lt;/strong&gt;: Ensure you&amp;rsquo;re using compatible versions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Permission issues&lt;/strong&gt;: Verify your account has the necessary permissions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>